Ruby1.9:
gem install ruby-mysql

Ruby 1.8
gem install mysql-ruby
change 
require "Mysql"
to
require "mysql"

gem install gpx
gem install libxml-ruby

Compiling imgkap:
gcc -I./FreeImage/Source/ imgkap.c -O3 -s -lm -lfreeimage -o imgkap

Compiing imgkap on a Mac:
gcc -I./FreeImage/Source/ imgkap.c -O3 -s -lstdc++ -lfreeimage -o imgkap

To build FreeImage 3.1.5.4 on a MAC, use the makefile from http://sourceforge.net/p/freeimage/bugs/228/
